info.description:
a modified version of style 1472 ( http://userstyles.org/styles/1472 ) ... 
the code is all the original code, with only the addition of code to center the listing in the middle of the page so it looks a little cleaner

200902.03 - minimized the header a bit, to pull all the main content up a bit... to view more on screen at a time;
200902.09 - removed the hours/time bar in the middle of the listing;

style.css:
@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);

@-moz-document domain("tv.yahoo.com") {
 #yui-main .yui-b {
  margin-left: auto !important; 
  margin-right: auto !important;
 }

 #hd, #gridright, #dtk-footernav, #ytv-uf, div.gtAd, div.northAd, a[name="page1"] + div.timeline, 
 div.north-container
{display: none !important; }

 div#gridheader {display: none !important;}
 a#tivo {float: none !important; display: table !important;}
 div.grid-pages {position: relative !important; top: -60px !important;}

 form.displayFav {
  float: right !important; 
  text-align: right !important; 
  top: -100px !important; 
  margin-right: 2px !important;
 }
 form.displayFav input[type=checkbox] {float: right !important;}
}
